# Angular Engineering Rules

- Use standalone components when practical; strong typing everywhere.
- Reactive forms over template forms for complex flows.
- Strict change detection; OnPush by default.

## Performance
- Prefer `async` pipe; avoid manual subscriptions without `takeUntil`.

## Security
- Use HttpClient with interceptors; sanitize HTML, enable CSP.

